skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inspire me
des:
This skill serves its user with an inspirational quote whenever the user asks for it.

Inspire Me will greet the user with inspirational quote when user says one of the following utterances:-
open inspire me
inspire me
motivate me
tell me something
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
